{
  "texts": [
    "The protocol for this study was registered on the Open Science Framework prior to study commencement (https:// osf. io/ 2kvs3).",
    "We planned to include PLSs from two more organizations (Joanna Briggs Institute and Evidence for Policy and Practice Information and Co-ordinating Centre).",
    "However, during the data collection phase, we discovered that those organizations have not yet published PLSs for their systematic reviews.",
    "An electronic mail was sent to the representatives of all six included organizations asking for all PLSs of their published systematic reviews.",
    "We received two replies."
  ]
}